{"tid":439302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋民直擊】白衣男大鬧菜街老麥 打職員兇食客：做乜昅我女朋友","createTime":"2017-10-17T16:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T00:27:43.000Z","uid":84436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"acb535fe2842453def5692aa4718263b00c6c094","tid":439302,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171017/57345031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171017%2F57345031&d=%2BStmu2oD2BmvbffMkvJrmUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c0086f77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171017%2F57345031&h=8d5b5a1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171017/57345031</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角西洋菜南街麥當勞發生打人事件！晚上9時許，餐廳內一名身穿白色上衣的男子，突然與旁邊的一對男女食客發生爭執，不斷大聲呼叫「做乜係咁昅我女朋友」，其間不斷講粗口並推跌餐廳內的枱凳。由於當時餐廳內坐滿食客，全部人都聞聲查看，麥當勞的經理亦趕至了解，惟白衣男亦不斷鬧事挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n讀者林先生當時正與朋友在麥當勞內用餐，他目睹白衣男不斷咆哮，情緒激動，又打傷麥當勞經理，他指白衣男鬧事不久後，一名身穿黑衫的男子上前阻止，將白衣男推跌在地上並出手掌摑。雖然與白衣男同行的女子不斷出言阻止，叫黑衣男「你唔好再冚佢喇，佢抽筋嫁」，又聲言會立即離開，但遭在場的職員阻止。他形容白衣男被摑後，身體一度僵硬，甚至抽筋近一分鐘，「無幾耐佢就冇乜事喇，但望落去就好似仲係好驚咁」，其後數名警員手持盾牌及警棍到場戒備，又向眾人落取口供。"},{"pid":"afefd2e9383f4ed1082ad330df25847f9e669439","tid":439302,"uid":53278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:26:54.000Z","msg":"痴線佬都有女"},{"pid":"24b0f15fc67ffc8dc65f04d913ac5564affca454","tid":439302,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"昅呀婆妹下妹下都唔昅你條女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c489375314ea2b45e93022d705c1881e6b1d46f","tid":439302,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"條女似係輕度智障，咁條仔一樣嘅機會都唔細"},{"pid":"fbf846c90c60f8a9fbc3668fd8ee45ab4166857b","tid":439302,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線佬都有女</blockquote><br />\n條女都似弱弱地智果隻"},{"pid":"3ed771dfebb26697fcd283cc54334e3024475bd8","tid":439302,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:31:33.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案"},{"pid":"1ca442059c18f3b0b9b739e77e2661fda7722607","tid":439302,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"弱智都有拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236c4dc49a41874871639a8494f19133fdfd43d1","tid":439302,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>弱智都有拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連狗都有閪屌嘅時候,我哋班連登毒撚連狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f018b729b314643d0dfce9e1034749d9b3e33e","tid":439302,"uid":87511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"警方表示，晚上9時許一名男子在旺角西洋菜南街的麥當勞內突然病發，推冧餐廳內的枱凳，有2名食客上前阻止並報警。警方到場時情況已經回復平靜，涉事男子不需到醫院檢查求醫，<span style=\"color: red;\">經調查後將案件列作「傻人發現」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n最柒莫過於一心搞事想威<br />\n點知畀人當做傻仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5931ce8b5f5eb080190dda7740eac2f90dbdbf7","tid":439302,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:22:42.000Z","msg":"最尾條女講果句野真係好應景"},{"pid":"6869cb36bf8e78c9e44b78a59fe5993cdb388bbb","tid":439302,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾條女講果句野真係好應景</blockquote><br />\n好鬼正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cf14a674d8f741e0b22a33f7361374aa0a06a9","tid":439302,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:26:42.000Z","msg":"黑衫男好兇"},{"pid":"47c5efc6e21de5ccbb060ec15905d7e998e0df6a","tid":439302,"uid":232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最尾條女講果句野真係好應景</blockquote><br />\n好鬼正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食花生食夠喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}